  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, DclfAlgorithm, IDclfAlgoLookup, IDclfResult, NameTag, NetworkRef<BaseAclfNetwork<?,?>>, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EDclfAlgorithmImpl, SenAnalysisAlgorithmImpl

    public class DclfAlgorithmImpl
extends NetworkRefImpl<BaseAclfNetwork<?,?>>
implements DclfAlgorithm
    An implementation of the model object 'Dc Loadflow'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Dclf Calculated
    • Apply Adjustment
    • Adj Max Iterations
    • Adj Tolerance
    • Acc Factor
    • Dclf Solver
    • Dclf Algo Bus List
    • Dclf Algo Branch List
